📘 BudgetWise – Milestone 1 Documentation
AI-Based Expense Forecasting Tool (Infosys Springboard Internship)
🧩 1. Project Overview

BudgetWise is a personal expense analysis and visualization tool developed as part of the Infosys Springboard Internship (Milestone 1).

This milestone focuses on understanding the fundamentals of data analysis using Python libraries — NumPy, Pandas, and Matplotlib.

The goal of this milestone is to:

Load and analyze expense data from a CSV file.

Calculate total and average expenses.

Visualize spending patterns through bar and line charts.

Build a foundation for AI-based expense forecasting in future milestones.

